# enabled|label|source_path|destination_mode|destination_value|sync_stop_file
# destination_mode values:
#   same-name   -> remote uses basename(source_path)
#   fixed       -> remote uses destination_value exactly
#   default-root -> remote uses FILE_DEFAULT_DESTINATION_ROOT/destination_value
